# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.0.3] - 2020-08-13
### Changed
- Refactored the code to be more readable
- Better modularity; API calls are now exclusively being made in designated functions
- Renamed helper_struct to cctray_data_struct, chose more speaking names upon modification

### Added
- A section about the CCTray format in the README


## [0.0.2] - 2020-08-12
### Changed
- All sensitive data is now passed via Environment variables

### Removed
- The venv/ directory as well as the cctray_example.xml file

## [0.0.1] - 2020-08-04
### Added
- Basic functionality; the script traverses through an organisation and gets the workflow jobs for all the repos
- The Github Token is being passed as an environment variable instead of being hardcoded
- For the most part, Github semantics are being matched to CCTray semantics
